      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it spotless and strictly following every service schedule. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new without the new-car price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
