    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously garaged and climate-controlled since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with a professional ceramic coating, showing absolutely zero swirl marks, chips, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery still carries that distinct new-car aroma, and every surface\u2014from the dashboard to the door cards\u2014is free of wear or sun damage. Mechanically, it is flawless, benefiting from a documented history of preventative maintenance performed exclusively by certified technicians. Every button, switch, and electronic system functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade investment for the discerning driver who accepts nothing less than perfection. Included are all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a comprehensive service binder.",
